Real Estate Associates Limited II: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 7:44 AM ET
Real Estate Management and Development

Company Overview of Real Estate Associates Limited II



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Real Estate Associates Limited II invests in other limited partnerships that own or lease, and operate federal, state, and local government-assisted housing projects in the United States. As of March 31, 2016, it held limited partnership interests in one local limited partnership that owned a residential low income rental project with 48 apartment units. National Partnership Investments Associates and National Partnership Investments, LLC serve as general partners of the company. The company was founded in 1979 and is based in Los Angeles, California.


PO Box 91274Los Angeles, CA 90009United StatesFounded in 1979



Phone: 720-387-8135








