Real Estate Associates Limited II Key Developments

Real Estate Associates Limited II announced delayed annual 10-K filing
Mar 30 16
On 03/30/2016, Real Estate Associates Limited II announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-K by the deadline required by the SEC.


