Real Estate Associates Limited III: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 7:44 AM ET
Real Estate Management and Development

Company Overview of Real Estate Associates Limited III



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Real Estate Associates Limited III invests in partnerships that primarily owns and operates federal, state, and local government-assisted housing projects in the United States. As of December 31, 2014, it had investments in one local partnership, which owned and rented a housing project. National Partnership Investments, LLC and National Partnership Investment Associates serve as general partners of the company. Real Estate Associates Limited III was founded in 1980 and is based in Los Angeles, California.


PO Box 91274Los Angeles, CA 90009United StatesFounded in 1980



Phone: 720-387-8135








