        Contact REAL



					REAL operate at the interface of investment, corporate real 
                    estate and finance worlds to significantly improve property 
                    returns and investment performance.
For fund investors we establish and operate 
                collective investment schemes allowing tax-efficient indirect 
                investment by a wide range of entities including corporate 
                pension funds, private investors, companies, SIPPs and SSASs.
For owners we provide asset and property management 
        services including advice on investment purchases and sales, with 
        bespoke accounting solutions and services for offshore entities.
For occupiers we align property tactics with 
        corporate strategy, to reduce costs, monitor risks, manage assets from 
        acquisition through to disposal, and provide services relating to 
        unwanted Legacy leaseholds.

Real Estate Associates Ltd, Warnford Court, 
        29 Throgmorton Street, 
        London EC2N 2AT  tel: +44(0)20 7947 4160 




